      "*": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b><a href=\"/Main_Page\" title=\"Main Page\">Home</a> * <a href=\"/Engines\" title=\"Engines\">Engines</a> * DON</b>\n</p><p><b>DON</b>,<br />\nan <a href=\"/UCI\" title=\"UCI\">UCI</a> compliant <a href=\"/Category:Open_Source\" title=\"Category:Open Source\">open source chess engine</a> by <a href=\"/index.php?title=Ehsan_Rashid&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Ehsan Rashid (page does not exist)\">Ehsan Rashid</a> <a href=\"/Category:Derivative\" title=\"Category:Derivative\">derived</a> from <a href=\"/Glaurung\" title=\"Glaurung\">Glaurung</a> and even more from its successor <a href=\"/Stockfish\" title=\"Stockfish\">Stockfish</a> \n<sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>, \ndistributed under the <a href=\"/Free_Software_Foundation#GPL\" title=\"Free Software Foundation\">GNU General Public License</a>. DON supports up to 512 cores for its <a href=\"/Parallel_Search\" title=\"Parallel Search\">parallel search</a>, and up to 1024 GiB of <a href=\"/Transposition_Table\" title=\"Transposition Table\">hash</a> <a href=\"/Memory\" title=\"Memory\">memory</a> including <a href=\"/Memory#HugePages\" title=\"Memory\">large pages</a> \n<sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>. Since August 2020, DON incorporates <a href=\"/NNUE\" title=\"NNUE\">NNUE</a> based on <a href=\"/Stockfish_NNUE\" title=\"Stockfish NNUE\">Stockfish NNUE</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup>. \n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Forum_Posts\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Forum Posts</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#External_Links\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">External Links</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#Chess_Engine\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Chess Engine</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#Misc\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Misc</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Forum_Posts\">Forum Posts</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=DON&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Forum Posts\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=51151\">DON 1.0b derivate Glaurung</a> by <a href=\"/Jose_Maria_Velasco\" title=\"Jose Maria Velasco\">Jose Mº Velasco</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, February 03, 2014</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=51259\">DON 1.0b With licensed</a> by <a href=\"/Jose_Maria_Velasco\" title=\"Jose Maria Velasco\">Jose Mº Velasco</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, February 12, 2014</li></ul>\n<dl><dd> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=51259&amp;start=7\">Re: DON 1.0b With licensed</a> by <a href=\"/index.php?title=Ehsan_Rashid&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Ehsan Rashid (page does not exist)\">Ehsan Rashid</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, February 22, 2014</dd></dl>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=72613&amp;start=320#p856640\">Re: New engine releases 2020...Don NNUE 2020?</a> by supersharp77, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, August 19, 2020</li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"External_Links\">External Links</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=DON&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: External Links\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Chess_Engine\">Chess Engine</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=DON&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: Chess Engine\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://github.com/erashid/DON\">erashid/DON · GitHub</a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Misc\">Misc</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=DON&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" title=\"Edit section: Misc\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Don\">Don from Wikipedia</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Don_(river)\">Don (river) from Wikipedia</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Don_River_(disambiguation)\">Don River (disambiguation) from Wikipedia</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Don_(honorific)\">Don (honorific) from Wikipedia</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=DON&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" title=\"Edit section: References\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=51151&amp;start=2\">Re: DON 1.0b derivate Glaurung</a> by <a href=\"/Marco_Costalba\" title=\"Marco Costalba\">Marco Costalba</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, February 03, 2014</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-2\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://github.com/erashid/DON/blob/master/Readme.md\">DON/Readme.md at master · erashid/DON · GitHub</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-3\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=72613&amp;start=320#p856640\">Re: New engine releases 2020...Don NNUE 2020?</a> by supersharp77, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, August 19, 2020</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div>\n<p><b><a href=\"/Engines\" title=\"Engines\">Up one Level</a></b>\n</p>\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260301020706\nCache expiry: 86400\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.008 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.008 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 65/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 138/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 0/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 0/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 2/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%    0.000      1 -total\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key oscar70_mw1-mw_:pcache:idhash:7506-0!canonical and timestamp 20260301020706 and revision id 22125\n -->\n"
